Interface RelationInstance

All Superinterfaces:
AnnotatedElement, DescriptionStatement, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IdentifiedElement, Instance, Member, NamedInstance, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Statement
All Known Implementing Classes:
RelationInstanceImpl
public interface RelationInstance extends NamedInstance
A representation of the model object 'Relation Instance'. RelationInstance is a named instance that can be typed by relation entities and that goes from one or more named instances as sources to one or more named instances as target.

The following features are supported:

  • Owned Types
  • Sources
  • Targets
